        java.util.ArrayList<java.util.ArrayList<FiloPod>> assign(java.util.ArrayList<java.util.ArrayList<FiloPod>> filo,
                                                         ij.ImagePlus imp)
        Assign track indexes to the passed ArrayList<ArrayList<FiloPod>>
        Links are assigned by setting the FiloPod track index fields.
        Parameters:
        filo - The FiloPod Collection for assignment. This is a List of timepoints each having a List of FiloPods.
        imp - The ImagePlus that the FiloPods came from
        Returns:
        the same ArrayList<ArrayList<FiloPod>> passed as filo with indexes assigned for convenience
